#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:2
msgid "协同过滤"
msgstr "Collaborative Filtering"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:4
msgid ""
"协同过滤模型基于用户-物品交互矩阵进行推荐，不依赖序列信息。 FreeRec 中的协同过滤模型继承自 "
":class:`~freerec.models.base.GenRecArch`。"
msgstr ""
"Collaborative filtering models make recommendations based on the user-item interaction matrix without relying on sequential information. "
"Collaborative filtering models in FreeRec inherit from :class:`~freerec.models.base.GenRecArch`."

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:8
msgid "MF-BPR"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Matrix Factorization with Bayesian Personalized Ranking** — 经典的矩阵分解模型， "
"使用 BPR 损失函数优化隐式反馈推荐的 pairwise 排序。"
msgstr ""
"**Matrix Factorization with Bayesian Personalized Ranking** -- A classic matrix factorization model "
"that uses the BPR loss function to optimize pairwise ranking for implicit feedback recommendation."

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:17
msgid "examples/MF-BPR/main.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:22 ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:48
msgid "**代码要点：**"
msgstr "**Code Highlights:**"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:24
msgid "**模型结构** ：用户和物品各一个 Embedding 层，直接内积计算相似度"
msgstr "**Model Architecture**: One Embedding layer each for users and items; similarity is computed via dot product"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:25
msgid "**训练管道** ：``choiced_user_ids_source`` 随机采样用户 → 正样本采样 → 负样本采样"
msgstr "**Training Pipeline**: ``choiced_user_ids_source`` randomly samples users -> positive sample sampling -> negative sample sampling"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:26
msgid "**排序缓存** ：``reset_ranking_buffers`` 在评估前预计算所有嵌入，避免重复计算"
msgstr "**Ranking Buffer**: ``reset_ranking_buffers`` precomputes all embeddings before evaluation to avoid redundant computation"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:27
msgid "**损失函数** ：BPR Loss，优化正样本得分高于负样本"
msgstr "**Loss Function**: BPR Loss, optimizing positive sample scores to be higher than negative samples"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:30
msgid "LightGCN"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:32
msgid ""
"**Simplifying Graph Convolution Network for Recommendation** — "
"轻量级图卷积推荐模型， 去除特征变换和非线性激活，仅保留邻域聚合操作。"
msgstr ""
"**Simplifying Graph Convolution Network for Recommendation** -- "
"A lightweight graph convolution recommendation model that removes feature transformation and nonlinear activation, retaining only neighborhood aggregation."

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:37
msgid "需要安装 ``torch-geometric``：``pip install freerec[graph]``"
msgstr "Requires ``torch-geometric``: ``pip install freerec[graph]``"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:43
msgid "examples/LightGCN/main.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:50
msgid "**图构建** ：``to_normalized_adj`` 从训练集构建对称归一化邻接矩阵，注册为 buffer"
msgstr "**Graph Construction**: ``to_normalized_adj`` builds a symmetric normalized adjacency matrix from the training set, registered as a buffer"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:51
msgid "**图卷积** ：``encode`` 方法执行多层邻域聚合，最终嵌入为各层的均值"
msgstr "**Graph Convolution**: The ``encode`` method performs multi-layer neighborhood aggregation; the final embedding is the mean across all layers"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:52
msgid ""
"**双损失** ：``fit`` 返回 ``(rec_loss, emb_loss)``，Coach 中以 ``weight_decay`` "
"加权合并"
msgstr ""
"**Dual Loss**: ``fit`` returns ``(rec_loss, emb_loss)``; combined in the Coach with ``weight_decay`` "
"weighting"

#: ../../tutorials/cf_rec.rst:53
msgid ""
"**自定义 Coach** ：``CoachForLightGCN`` 重写了 ``set_optimizer`` 以禁用 PyTorch 内置 "
"weight_decay（改由 emb_loss 手动控制正则化）"
msgstr ""
"**Custom Coach**: ``CoachForLightGCN`` overrides ``set_optimizer`` to disable PyTorch's built-in "
"weight_decay (regularization is manually controlled via emb_loss instead)"
